INSTALLATION and RUNNING:

1) NetfilterQueue. GO TO: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/NetfilterQueue
2) netaddr. GO TO: http://pythonhosted.org/netaddr/installation.html
3) Mininet: GO TO: http://mininet.org/download/

4) INSTALL:
sudo apt-get install build-essential python-dev libnetfilter-queue-dev
sudo pip install NetfilterQueue
sudo pip install netaddr
sudo pip install networkx

5) Run the following commands to upgrade the Mininet OVS instance to the latest v2.0:
sudo apt-get install python-software-properties software-properties-common
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:mighost/ppa
sudo apt-get update
/etc/init.d/openvswitch-switch stop
/etc/init.d/openvswitch-controller stop
sudo apt-get install openvswitch-common  openvswitch-datapath-dkms  openvswitch-switch
/etc/init.d/openvswitch-switch start

6) execute: sudo ./runCmds
(in case of failure, run: chmod +x runCmds)
once fininshed, the figures are generated in fattree44_32h folder.

For any question conatact: yanivb@il.ibm.com
